Dynamo's Seeing is Believing SA Tour begins in Pretoria at Time Square, Menlyn on Friday, 11 May 2018 at 20:00 followed by two shows on Saturday, 12 May 2018 at 15:00 and 20:00. There will also be one final Pretoria show on Sunday, 13 May 2018 at 15:00. The three Cape Town performances begin on Friday, 18 May 2018 at 20:00 and continue on Saturday, 19 May 2018 at 15:00 and 20:00. All Mother City shows will take place at the Grand Arena, GrandWest. All tickets are on sale at Computicket. MORE ABOUT DYNAMO: With over 127 shows and more than 600 000 tickets sold across global arenas, master magician Dynamo brings one of the largest scale magic shows in the world to South Africa. Dynamo has visited SA several times and even recorded an episode of his world renowned television series, Dynamo: Magician Impossible featuring locals from Khayelitsha, Cape Town, Soweto and Johannesburg. DYNAMO SA TOUR INFORMATION: PRETORIA - VENUE: Sun Arena at Time Square, Menlyn Friday, 11 May 2018 at 20:00Saturday, 12 May 2018 at 15:00 and 20:00Sunday, 13 May 2018 at 15:00 TICKET PRICES: R379, R429, R480, R581, R682CAPE TOWN - VENUE: Grand Arena, GrandWest Friday, 18 May 2018 at 20:00Saturday, 19 May 2018 at 15:00 and 20:00 TICKET PRICES: R379, R429, R480, R581, R682 Source: Supplied